description: Perfect for a weeknight dinner, these tortillas are fun to assemble and will have everyone at the table reaching for more.
keywords: Tortilla,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Quick Chicken Tortillas Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g Cook chicken breast stir-fry strips Mexican style

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large frying pan over medium heat. Add chicken and cook, stirring occasionally, for 12 minutes or until cooked through. Transfer to a chopping board and roughly chop. Transfer to a bowl and cover to keep warm.
Add corn to pan and cook, stirring occasionally, for 3 minutes or until beginning to char. Transfer to a small bowl. Clean out frying pan.
Place slaw and dressing from kit in a separate bowl. Toss well to combine.

Open tortilla packet and remove and discard freshness sachet. Heat pan over medium-high heat, then cook one tortilla for 10 seconds each side or until golden. Transfer to a plate and cover to keep warm. Repeat with remaining tortillas. Divide chicken, corn and slaw mixtures among tortillas. Serve.
